  <div class="container-narrow">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'Learn', href: '/learn/' },
      { label: 'Guides', href: '/learn/guides/' },
      { label: 'Entity Seo For Ai' }
    ]} />

    <p class="section-tag">Guide</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">Entity SEO for AI Search</h1>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Entity SEO is the practice of building a clear, consistent, and well-connected entity that AI systems can understand and recommend. It is the bridge between traditional SEO and AI search visibility.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Brands with strong entity signals are 4x more likely to appear in AI recommendations. A business can have high page authority and low entity authority – ranking strongly in Google while being nearly invisible in AI answers.</p>
    <h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">What Is an Entity?</h2>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">An entity, in the way AI systems understand the word, is a distinct thing in the world with clear attributes and relationships. A business is an entity. A person is an entity. A product is an entity. When AI systems encounter enough consistent, cross-referenced information about an entity from enough trusted sources, they build a stable internal representation of it.</p>
    <h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">How to Build Entity Authority</h2>
    <div class="space-y-4 mb-10">
      <div class="card-teal-border"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2">Consistent description everywhere</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Same language, same entity sentence across every platform and directory. Inconsistency creates uncertainty.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2">Structured data</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Organisation schema with sameAs links anchors the entity and connects every ecosystem signal back to the canonical source.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2">Wikidata and Knowledge Graph</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">A Wikidata entry and presence in Google's Knowledge Graph are the most formalised expressions of entity authority.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2">Independent citations</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Multiple independent sources describing the business consistently. Directories, press, reviews, publications – each is a vote of confidence.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>

